name: Consultation
description: Schedule a consultation with me so I can get to know you and your dog. We'll discuss your needs and goals and then go over my training methods so we can begin to construct a training plan together!

name: Monday Pack Hike
description:

name: Real-World Proofing Your Dog ~ Week 1, 2, & 3
description:
"Proofing" in dog training means ensuring your dog will follow commands even in a distracting or challenging places. You can work on problems & get feed-back & moral support from other dog owners in a supportive small-group setting. Each week we'll work on different training strategies & activities to find something that's fun & works for you & your dog.
Week 1: Impulse Control
Week 2: Social Behaviors
Week 3: Real-World Proofing

name: Real-World Proofing Your Dog ~ Week 1: Impulse Control
description: In week 1, we will cover the potentially life-saving "Leave It" command as well as longer, stronger sit/stays, & recall.

name: Real-World Proofing Your Dog ~ Week 2: Social Behaviors
description:
Work on problems & get feed-back & moral support from other dog owners in a supportive small-group setting. Each week we'll work on different training strategies & activities to find something that's fun & works well for you & your dog.
In Week 2, we will cover critical social behaviors like greeting strangers (or just walking past) calmly, appropriate dog park play, & addressing excessive barking or jumping behavior.

name: Real-World Proofing Your Dog ~ Week 3: Real-World Proofing
description:
Work on problems & get feed-back & moral support from other dog owners in a supportive small-group setting. Each week we'll work on different training strategies & activities to find something that's fun & works well for you & your dog.
in week 3, we will take the skills of the previous weeks to the next level. We might meet as a group in a new, near-by location or at a busier time of day or week to test & strengthen yours & your dogs skills.
